    <p>New Mexico Office of the Superintendent of Insurance (OSI) data shows elevated non-renewal complaint rates in Taos, Mora, San Miguel, and Rio Arriba counties post-2022. Premium increases of 30 to 80 percent above 2020 levels have been documented in WUI-adjacent ZIP codes where admitted coverage is still available.</p>
